Package: roeference
Type: Package
Title: rOEference: Easy Acces to Some Flemish Reference and Heritage Datasets 
Version: 0.0.0.9004
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = 'Maarten',
          family = 'Vermeyen',
          role = c('aut', 'cre'),
          email = 'maarten.vermeyen@vlaanderen.be',
          comment = c(orcid = '0000-0003-1197-6562')),
    person("Agentschap Onroerend Erfgoed", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
  )
Maintainer: Maarten Vermeyen <maarten@vermeyen.xyz>
Description: This package provides helper functions to download and load some
   Flemish public (geographic) reference datasets such as administrative units, as 
   well as the public geographic datasets of the Flemish Heritage agency 
   (agentschap Onroerend Erfgoed).
